Set yourself free from the Matrix. How to install GrapheneOS on an Android phone.
Works only on Pixel phones. By the cheapest refurbished phone first. If you like it, get a new unlocked phone. You can get a new SIM card and number with unlimited data for $45 every three months from Mint Mobile.
Take the red pill.
